{"tid":2209805,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專家：三大侵略手段 危機波及全球","createTime":"2020-09-20T02:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T02:24:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ae35253ee1af69324e6c9eaeb0e0a9fa08b3e2a1","tid":2209805,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:04:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/TNTXOLFPGNBNLLYH6L35GHR2D4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FTNTXOLFPGNBNLLYH6L35GHR2D4%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE76sSahl6lMEnfwETMIwf14%3D&h=778635d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FTNTXOLFPGNBNLLYH6L35GHR2D4%2F&h=0b52bc54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/TNTXOLFPGNBNLLYH6L35GHR2D4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n專家：三大侵略手段 危機波及全球<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lITXwWj6RWOgXA0AshZHj2VH5qc=/2105x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SRP5CZR4IFCZTPKAITGJGM26KU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlITXwWj6RWOgXA0AshZHj2VH5qc%3D%2F2105x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSRP5CZR4IFCZTPKAITGJGM26KU.jpg&h=02be82d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台海局勢緊張，危機四伏。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中國大陸文攻武嚇台灣引起歐洲關注，《德國之聲》訪問多名專家，製作一小時影片，分析解放軍侵台的三種可能性，呼籲歐洲國家及早做準備。<br />\n<br />\n片段點出中國可能侵犯台灣的三種情景，包括混合戰、如俄國併吞克里米亞的方式突擊台灣，以及全面入侵台灣。。。。。。。。。。。。。。第二種是仿效俄羅斯吞併克里米亞方式，以突擊方式佔領台灣總統府及行政院，扶植傀儡政府宣佈「公投」，然後全台灣併入中國大陸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呼籲歐洲及早防範<br />\n<br />\n第三種就是真正的「武統台灣」，以武裝全力入侵。《德國之聲》指出，武統台灣不僅是台灣的危機，更是全世界的危機，。。。。。。。。。。。。報道認為三大原因均顯示了國際社會太過輕忽台灣所遭受的中國威脅，不夠關注中國的野心，呼籲歐洲國家及早做準備。<br />\n<br />\n軍事評論員黃東向本報分析，混合式及武統台灣較有機會。他指出，大陸現時已一直使用混合式，亦是現時的首選，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。大，但以台灣的軍力，防守一星期是毋庸置疑，加上美軍的轟炸機在關島亦一日可至，可阻礙登陸，相信令武統難度增加不少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OSN-w-Zhpd7N2fcYToSRSAyzixk=/898x1805/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OCWXOZWZLJDTPP5PDOVLKGL7VE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOSN-w-Zhpd7N2fcYToSRSAyzixk%3D%2F898x1805%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOCWXOZWZLJDTPP5PDOVLKGL7VE.gif&h=55b34e0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1085033258d477ea837fd8aa3cb94faa5696facd","tid":2209805,"uid":22893,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"本來一做得幾好，溫水煮蛙，又係要多謝柒婆大波驊送中"},{"pid":"5c756d1f432130ee2adcde3223493de71f2e0081","tid":2209805,"uid":54511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1085033258d477ea837fd8aa3cb94faa5696facd","tid":2209805,"uid":22893,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"本來一做得幾好，溫水煮蛙，又係要多謝柒婆大波驊送中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DaW6HAq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDaW6HAq.jpg&h=728c3c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m1h5X8P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm1h5X8P.gif&h=c0cb5450&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3fbbf40cdfd8ed8818d27f9ea663bed0e03b1c","tid":2209805,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/52842320_2137178186368803_2768383035345731584_o.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=96sXT_jHYp0AX_R6zn4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=ae8ad5bc3f0865285c0ece326ccb24ec&amp;oe=5F8ABCA2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F52842320_213717818636880